data.description: Beautiful Homestead on 5.28 Acres with large Pole Barn! This 4-bedroom home lives large due it's open concept on the main floor with large rooms surrounding the staircase. Full of upgrades, the brand-new kitchen is the centerpiece and heart of the house with new cabinets, new stainless steel Samsung appliances, butcher block countertops and a large farm sink. The kitchen is open to the breakfast area and the formal dining room, which provides a great space for entertainment. The large living room boasts a large bay window with views of the expansive front yard where one can sit by the wood burning fireplace watching the wildlife outside. Around the corner is the family room that could double as an office space. Surrounding the family room outside is a cozy screened-in porch, great for hanging out on Summer evenings. The four bedrooms are tucked upstairs with two full bathrooms providing great privacy from the entertainment below. Among other upgrades are new flooring, new paint, new recessed lighting, new lighting fixtures, new deck, new trap doors to the basement and the brand-new 24'x 36' metal Pole Barn, perfect for boat storage or a workshop. Upgrades performed within the past 10 years include the roof and gutters, siding and furnace. The basement is unfinished and so it's the large unfinished attic space above the main living area, which is great for storage. This home has it all! It's situated in the quiet countryside, but only 5 minutes from Ellettsville with easy access to State Road 46. Grade A schools. High speed internet access via SCI REMC fiber. Hooked on City water and natural gas. Comcast also available. Great home with acreage! Excluded from the sale are the freezer, the washer and dryer.
